data.description: Welcome to the Spectrum Gilbert neighborhood! Backing up to the tennis courts, this home provides plenty of privacy and quiet. The elementary school is right around the corner, and shopping is conveniently located just blocks away along the 202. You'll love the lifestyle this location provides, with top-rated schools within the community and plenty of neighborhood parks to enjoy. As soon as you enter, you'll be immediately impressed by the spacious and open concept floor plan. With a separate living room and family room, this home provides ample space for your family and guests to enjoy. The newer wood floors throughout the house give a beautiful uniformity and cleanliness to this stunning home, which also features a gas stove for all your cooking needs. Heading upstairs to the second level, you'll find all the bedrooms including the master bedroom separated from the other rooms with a loft. The master bedroom is the perfect place to retreat after a long day, with plenty of space and a beautifully appointed ensuite. The other rooms provide plenty of space for your family to grow and thrive. This gorgeous home also has a low maintenance backyard with a fire pit that's perfect for entertaining, and it even leads to the greenbelt for easy access to local parks.This is truly a great and spacious home that will provide you and your family with years of enjoyment. Don't miss your chance to make it yours!
